research_municipality_step.notes: Buda, TX operates under a council-manager form of government. There was conflicting information regarding the Council Member for Single Member District C across different snippets from the official city website. One snippet listed Kimberly Goodman, while another listed Terry Cummings. The Texas Municipal League also lists Terry Cummings for District C. Terry Cummings was chosen for the JSON object based on the more recent appearance in the search results from the official website and corroboration from the Texas Municipal League.
